**Update existing tests** (lines 1710-1855): Add `&HashMap::new()` as the fourth argument to all `compute_incremental_plan()` calls and `&HashMap::new()` as the third argument to `compute_deep_fingerprints()` calls. Approximately 10 test call sites.

